Spike Feresten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spike_Feresten 0 Michael Donovan "Spike" Feresten Jr. is an American television writer, screenwriter, comedian and television personality, who is best known for his work on Seinfeld, writing for David Letterman, and hosting the late night Talkshow with Spike Feresten from 2006 to 2009 on Fox. He is currently the host of Esquire Network's series Car Matchmaker with Spike Feresten.
